14:55.895 --> 14:58.966
to a lot of people.

14:58.999 --> 15:01.468
But I understand that beat about

15:01.501 --> 15:03.503
doing what you got to do
for your family.

15:06.073 --> 15:08.075
Five minutes, ladies.

15:11.278 --> 15:14.047
